Package dataframe.composite

Class Directory

java.lang.Object
dataframe.composite.Directory
All Implemented Interfaces:
IComponent
public class Directory
extends java.lang.Object
implements IComponent
Directory class needed to implement a composite pattern. Might contain several dataframes or/and other directories inside. Some methods might not function if labels are not equal (sort and query)
